 ('km_panadol', 'cat_pain_killers', 'Panadol', 'Paracetamol', 'GSK Kenya', '500mg', 'Tablet', 150, 0, 500, '', 'Fast-acting pain and fever relief. Kenya''s most trusted pain reliever.', 'Headache, fever, muscle aches, dental pain, period pain', '1-2 tablets every 4-6 hours. Max 8 tablets in 24 hours.', 'Rare: nausea, skin rash. Overdose causes liver damage.', 'Do not exceed recommended dose. Avoid with liver disease.', 'Store below 25°C', 0, 1, 4.8),
